{"tid":1944042,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔離登新風向: 放棄抗爭, 停止運動","createTime":"2020-03-26T06:48:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T12:07:03.000Z","uid":134071,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a2c71170e4523be511b788b439e591533cea74d9","tid":1944042,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T06:48:47.000Z","msg":"近日隔離登突然多左post叫人放棄抗爭, 停止運動... 而且仲得到大量正評. &nbsp; (而且佢地唔只屌連登, 仲炮轟埋tg....)<br />\n<br />\n老實講, 佢地既批評唔係完全無道理, 但都唔係支持「放棄抗爭, 停止運動」 既理由. <br />\n世界上最毒的說話, 係 &quot;大部分&quot;真話 加上 &quot;小部分&quot;危言聳聽 ; 但偏偏果&quot;少部分&quot;先係重點, 而且係最毒.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7206468/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7206468%2Fpage%2F1&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR8eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=6d25815b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7206468/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7208809/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7208809%2Fpage%2F1&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR8eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=b8d308ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7208809/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"32df62c448e5b8db7b3a05adb6b0f6b74e639c34","tid":1944042,"uid":134071,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T06:48:53.000Z","msg":"另一方面, 梁天琦都講過要有耐性.<br />\n<br />\n梁天琦: &quot;香港革命&quot;可能需要16年的時間, 才會成功<br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1377586/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1377586/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"c6c67b44393be1efe7e93aff10694a32c8460539","tid":1944042,"uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T06:54:14.000Z","msg":"任何批評都可睇下, 思想一下<br />\n<br />\n但不要 放棄抗爭, 停止運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d9be59b56115f80259f1f0538c887c63a43975e","tid":1944042,"uid":125168,"like":6,"dislike":0,"